author: Russell Brand
description:
Hospital staff are opting out. A bombshell UK report shows nearly 9 in 10 workers at a major NHS trust refused the flu shot—after years of mandates, shaming, and shifting promises. We trace how “trust the science” became a marketing slogan: coercion during COVID, indemnified pharma profits, censored dissent, and a proposed WHO treaty that would centralize emergency powers. The result isn’t ignorance—it’s a revolt from insiders who saw the system up close and won’t play along.
